      "text": "We’re delighting in the joy our kids are experiencing. Their passion for their research is palpable. The impact of following personal curiosity authentically and being given opportunities to be heard and seen is powerful. Throughout a DIG journey, our learners are prompted to notice surprise, delight and wonder. We’re consciously capturing and emphasises the emotions attached to their learning process. We’re making the feelings connected to learning overt and its working to deepen personal connections and making the emotional journey of learning explicit."
